titles = ['Distance vs. Day of Week separated by Age Group',
          'Speed vs. Day of Week separated by Age Group',
          'Trip Duration vs. Day of Week separated by Age Group']
ylabels = ['Distance (km)', 'Speed (km/hr)', 'Trip Duration (min)']
